a-curfew-twitter-reacts-with-memes-and-jokes-6323555/|accessdate=|author=|date=2020-03-20|format=|publisher=|language=|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200321164759/https://indianexpress.com/article/trending/trending-in-india/coronavirus-modi-announces-janata-curfew-twitter-reacts-with-memes-and-jokes-6323555/|archive-date=2020-03-21|access-date=2020-03-22}}</ref>甚至还有人创建了一个Facebook小组，作为年轻人（主要是[[Z世代|Z世代]]）分享创建和了解大流行病[[網路迷因|模因]]的空间。这个小组的名字叫“自我隔离的Zoom Memes”，截至到2020年4月，这个小组已经拥有超过500,000名成员。 该组织运用[[Zoom|Zoom]]为成千上万被迫线上学习的年轻人提供娱乐，帮助他们度过了闲暇的课余时间并教会他们如何应对现阶段的现状。 <ref>{{cite web|script-title=Humor in the face of coronavirus|trans-title=面对冠状病毒的幽默|url=https://www.dailytargum.com/article/2020/03/humor-in-the-face-of-global-pandemic|accessdate=2020-09-25|author=|date=|format=|publisher=|language=|dead-url=no|website=The Daily Targum|archive-date=2020-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200728233544/https://www.dailytargum.com/article/2020/03/humor-in-the-face-of-global-pandemic}}</ref>

